net.sf.jclec.mo.evaluation.fitness

Interface IGrEAMOFitness

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICrowdingDistanceMOFitness, IHypercubeMOFitness, INSGA2MOFitness
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GrEAMOFitness

    public interface IGrEAMOFitness
extends INSGA2MOFitness, IHypercubeMOFitness
    This interface defines the methods that the fitness of a solution should provide if the strategy use some of the procedures defined by the GrEA algorithm.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    GrEA, INSGA2MOFitness, IHypercubeMOFitness
